org.apache.drill.test

Class ClientFixture

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.drill.test.ClientFixture
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable

    public class ClientFixture
extends Object
implements AutoCloseable
    Represents a Drill client. Provides many useful test-specific operations such as setting system options, running queries, and using the @{link TestBuilder} class.
    See Also:
    ExampleTest for usage examples

      • setControls

        public void setControls(String controls)
        Set a set of injection controls that apply on the next query only. That query should be your target query, but may accidentally be an ALTER SESSION, EXPLAIN, etc. So, call this just before the SELECT statement.
        Parameters:
        controls - the controls string created by Controls.newBuilder() builder.
